body_html:
Hi Folks,
After this commit when I try to run tensorflow/contrib/lite/download_dependencies.sh it gives following error:
downloading https://mirror.bazel.build/bitbucket.org/eigen/eigen/get/b6e6d0cf6a77.tar.gz
tar: Unrecognized archive format
tar: Error exit delayed from previous errors.

I rolled back one commit to be able to successfully run it.

Regards,
Hovhannes
